1. How to build a ctags
go to the directory where you want the tag to be build
$ cd <folder>
$ ctags -R *

2. To search for a particular tag 
$ vim -t <tag>

3. How to set the path of the tags in vim
set tags=/path/to/dir

4. To go the definition of tag
  ctrl + ]

5. To go back to the previous window of tag
ctrl + T

6. 
